OL,3,C'Life changing' wearable Tourette's
OL,4,Cdevice shown to reduce tics
OL,6,FThe device, which is worn around the
OL,7,Fwrist like a watch, is due to be
OL,8,Freleased next year and has even been
OL,9,Ftested by the singer Lewis Capaldi,
OL,10,Fwho was diagnosed with Tourette's in
OL,11,F2022.
OL,13,FResearchers said it helped Capaldi
OL,14,F"feel calmer and clearly suppressed
OL,15,Fthe head and shoulder tics which can
OL,16,Fbe quite painful for him".
