OL,3,C'Life changing' wearable Tourette's
OL,4,Cdevice shown to reduce tics
OL,6,FRen Barons, who lives with Tourette's
OL,7,Fin Jersey, says: "I tried the device
OL,8,Fand it was really emotional. It was
OL,9,Flike a giant weight was lifted off my
OL,10,Fshoulders. The big thing for me is in
OL,11,Fhigh-stress situations.
OL,13,F"My tics are mostly now facial, so I
OL,14,Fdo movements with my eyes. However,
OL,15,Fsome people with Tourette's can't even
OL,16,Fgo out the house."
