OL,7,FOfficer for Neupulse, says: "The first
OL,8,Fperson I saw wearing the device said
OL,9,Fshe felt peace and that reaction was
OL,10,Fjust incredible. It's emotional every
OL,11,Ftime and literally life-changing for
OL,12,Fpeople."
